@startuml seq-email-signup
title Email/Password Signup

actor Parent as P
participant "Next.js PWA" as PWA
participant "Fastify API\nAuthController" as API
participant "AuthService" as Auth
participant "Keycloak" as KC
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "COPPAService" as COPPA

P -> PWA : Fill signup form\n(email, password)
PWA -> API : POST /auth/register
API -> Auth : createUser(email, password)
Auth -> KC : POST /admin/realms/.../users
KC --> Auth : 201 Created (keycloakId)
Auth -> DB : INSERT Account\n(email, keycloakId, role=PARENT,\nconsentStatus=PENDING)
Auth --> API : account created

API -> COPPA : initiateConsent(accountId)
COPPA -> DB : INSERT ConsentRecord\n(method=pending)
COPPA --> API : consent flow URL

API --> PWA : 201 { accountId,\nconsentRequired: true }
PWA --> P : Redirect to\nconsent verification

@enduml
